sequenceDiagram
    participant Browser
    participant LocalCache as Local DNS Cache
    participant Resolver as Recursive Resolver
    participant Root as Root Name Server
    participant TLD as TLD Name Server
    participant Auth as Authoritative Name Server

    Browser->>LocalCache: Query: example.com?
    alt Cache hit
        LocalCache-->>Browser: Return cached IP (TTL valid)
    else Cache miss
        LocalCache->>Resolver: Forward query: example.com?
        Resolver->>Root: Who handles .com?
        Root-->>Resolver: TLD server: a.gtld-servers.net
        Resolver->>TLD: Who handles example.com?
        TLD-->>Resolver: Authoritative: ns1.example.com
        Resolver->>Auth: What is the IP for example.com?
        Auth-->>Resolver: A record: 93.184.216.34 (TTL 3600)
        Resolver-->>LocalCache: Cache result with TTL
        LocalCache-->>Browser: 93.184.216.34
    end
    Note over Browser: Opens TCP connection to 93.184.216.34
